🧠 Prompting in Generative AI – Summary
Foundation models use prompts (inputs) to generate outputs (responses).
They are highly flexible, especially multimodal models, accepting inputs like text, images, code, etc.

🔑 Examples
- Question → Answer
- Text → Image
- Document → Summary
- Code with errors → Fixed code

⚙️ Key Insight
- The quality of the prompt directly impacts the output.
- Designing effective prompts is called prompt engineering.

